Requirement:

1. Two types of users: Admin and Customer.
2. User should be able to create an account.
3. Admin should be able to register a new Hotel and rooms for it.
4. Admin should be able to add new rooms for an existing Hotel.
5. Customer should be able to get all available hotels using location name.
7. Customer should be able to get all the rooms available in a hotel.
8. Customer should be able to book a room.

